welcome_message_body: "Welcome to beautiful Bainbridge Island! Known for its breathtaking views and charming small town feel, we invite you to explore and experience all that our island has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The north terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves private and charter flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The south terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves cargo and general aviation flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Bremerton Airport is reserved for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves domestic flights for Alaska Airlines and its partners.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves international flights for Delta Air Lines and its partners.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including dining options and rental car services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport provides a luxurious and exclusive experience for private jet travelers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
